org.opensocial.client
Class OpenSocialRequestParameter

java.lang.Object
  org.opensocial.client.OpenSocialRequestParameter

public class OpenSocialRequestParameter
extends java.lang.Object

An object which represents an OpenSocial data request parameter. Parameters can be single- or multi-valued (e.g. count is single-valued while fields can have one or more values) or single- or multi-keyed.

Author:
apijason@google.com (Jason Cooper)
